Back in my day champions had passive abilities as the entire ability!

{{champion:17}} {{champion:110}} 

I suppose when Riot gets to reworking these guys they'll give them 5 blinks and true damage based in their own health or some such nonsense.

{{champion:150}} can be an adc, a jungler, a mid, a sup (i've tried it), and a top lane and I've won with all.

{{champion:76}} can mid, top, jungle with high win stats, and sup. I bet if someone tried, she could even adc like Kog'Maw.

